 268	### 4. Background Jobs
 269	
 270	1. **Define job processor**:
 271	 ```typescript
 272	 @Process('job-name')
 273	 async handleJob(job: Job<JobData>) {
 274	 // Job implementation
 275	 }
 276	 ```
 277	
 278	2. **Queue job**:
 279	 ```typescript
 280	 await this.queue.add('job-name', jobData);
 281	 ```
 282	
