- ✅ Java files (`.java`) → `Language.JAVA`
- ✅ TypeScript files (`.ts`, `.tsx`) → `Language.TYPESCRIPT`
- ✅ JavaScript files (`.js`, `.jsx`) → `Language.JAVASCRIPT`
- ✅ Fallback to metadata framework detection

