 74	 * 
 75	 * Architecture:
 76	 * - Wraps Langfuse SDK for controlled access
 77	 * - Uses AsyncLocalStorage for automatic context propagation
 78	 * - Implements data sanitization before sending data
 79	 * - Provides no-op mode for zero overhead when disabled
 80	 * - Supports prompt management and versioning
 81	 * - Includes comprehensive error handling and recovery
 82	 * 
 83	 * Features:
 84	 * - Zero-config tracing that just works
 85	 * - Automatic PII detection and redaction
