 45	/**
 46	 * Core interface for the Langfuse integration module.
 47	 * 
 48	 * This module wraps the Langfuse SDK to provide controlled access, automatic 
 49	 * context management, and seamless integration with the AgentHub module system. 
 50	 * The goal is to make tracing completely transparent to agent developers.
 51	 * 
 52	 * Key features:
 53	 * - Wrapped Langfuse SDK for controlled access
 54	 * - Automatic trace context management
 55	 * - Span nesting without manual management
 56	 * - Prompt versioning and management
 57	 * - Async context propagation
 58	 * - Data sanitization before sending
 59	 * - No-op mode when disabled
 60	 * 
