 53	## Key Design Principles
 54	
 55	### 1. Module Independence
 56	Each module:
 57	- Has its own interface
 58	- Manages its own configuration
 59	- Can be tested in isolation
 60	- Has no direct dependencies on other modules
 61	
 62	### 2. Controlled Access
 63	- All external libraries are wrapped
 64	- No direct access from agents to third-party code
 65	- Consistent error handling
 66	- Unified monitoring
 67	
 68	### 3. Centralized Management
 69	- Session/state in one module
 70	- Configuration through AgentHub core
 71	- Module lifecycle managed centrally
 72	- Unified monitoring and metrics
 73	
 74	### 4. Testing at Each Step
 75	Each implementation includes:
 76	- Unit tests for the module
 77	- Integration tests with mock dependencies
 78	- Performance benchmarks
 79	- Error scenario testing
 80	
