 93	 * - Time complexity: O(n log n) where n = message count
 94	 * - Memory: O(k) where k = batch size (default: 100)
 95	 * - Throughput: ~10,000 messages/second on standard hardware
 96	 * 
 97	 * Trade-offs:
 98	 * - Batching adds 10-50ms latency
 99	 * - Reduces memory pressure by 80% vs processing all at once
 100	 */
