 3	## Context
 4	You are implementing the Module Registry - the central system that manages the lifecycle of all modules in AgentHub. This registry is responsible for module registration, dependency management, initialization order, health monitoring, and providing controlled access to modules. It ensures modules are initialized in the correct order, handles circular dependencies, and provides a unified interface for module discovery and access.
