 921	## Testing Requirements
 922	
 923	### 1. Unit Tests
 924	- Module registration and retrieval
 925	- Dependency resolution
 926	- Circular dependency detection
 927	- Initialization order
 928	- Health monitoring
 929	
 930	### 2. Integration Tests
 931	- Full module lifecycle
 932	- Module reloading
 933	- Error recovery
 934	- Graceful shutdown
 935	- Health aggregation
 936	
 937	### 3. Performance Tests
 938	- Module initialization time
 939	- Registry lookup performance
 940	- Health check overhead
 941	- Memory usage with many modules
 942	
 943	## Post-Implementation Validation
 944	
 945	### 1. Functionality Checklist
 946	- [ ] Modules register correctly
 947	- [ ] Dependencies are resolved
 948	- [ ] Circular dependencies detected
 949	- [ ] Initialization order is correct
 950	- [ ] Health monitoring works
 951	- [ ] Hot reload functions (dev)
 952	
 953	### 2. Reliability Requirements
 954	- [ ] Graceful error handling
 955	- [ ] Proper shutdown sequence
 956	- [ ] No resource leaks
 957	- [ ] Recovery from failures
 958	
 959	### 3. Performance Requirements
 960	- [ ] Fast module lookup (<1ms)
 961	- [ ] Efficient dependency resolution
 962	- [ ] Minimal health check overhead
 963	- [ ] Scales to 100+ modules
 964	
 965	## Common Pitfalls to Avoid
 966	
 967	1. **Don't ignore initialization order** - Dependencies must initialize first
 968	2. **Don't allow circular dependencies** - Detect and prevent
 969	3. **Don't block on health checks** - Run asynchronously
 970	4. **Don't leak resources** - Proper cleanup on shutdown
 971	5. **Don't hardcode module list** - Use factories for flexibility
 972	6. **Don't skip error boundaries** - Isolate module failures
 973	
 974	## Final Validation Questions
 975	
 976	1. Are all dependencies properly resolved?
 977	2. Is the initialization order deterministic?
 978	3. Does health monitoring provide useful insights?
 979	4. Can modules be reloaded without affecting others?
 980	5. Is the registry performant with many modules?
 981	6. Are module failures properly isolated?
 982	
 983	## Next Steps
 984	After completing the Module Registry, update the base agent implementation (07-base-agent-implementation.md) to use the modular architecture.
